  "data": {
    "title": "CloudTalk Tips: Best Ways to Boost Sales & Support Calls",
    "excerpt": "Discover proven CloudTalk tips and best practices to streamline your sales and support calls. See why 2,500+ teams trust this cloud call center. Try it today.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
        "url": "https://tonyciencia.com/blog/cloudtalk-tips.jpg",
        "alt": "CloudTalk Tips: Best Ways to Boost Sales & Support Calls",
        "filename": "cloudtalk-tips.jpg"
      }
    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://cloudtalk.io"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you run a sales team, a support desk, or both, you already know the pain: dropped calls, scattered notes, zero visibility into what your agents are actually doing. I've tested a handful of cloud call center tools over the past year, and ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CloudTalk",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "[^AFF1] keeps earning its spot on my shortlist. Below, I'm sharing the tips and best practices I've picked up — the stuff that actually moves the needle once you're inside the platform.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "*Disclosure: Some links below are affiliate links. If you sign up through them, I may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.*",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Why CloudTalk Stands Out in a Crowded Market",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Plenty of tools promise \"enterprise-grade calling for every team.\" Most of them overpromise and underdeliver. CloudTalk is different for three reasons:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Global reach without the headaches.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " You get local numbers in 160+ countries. I set up a UK, US, and German line for a client's sales team in under 20 minutes — no carrier contracts, no telecom jargon.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Speed to value.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " The onboarding is genuinely fast. Agents can start making calls the same day you sign up. No 6-week implementation saga.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Intelligence baked in.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " CloudTalk's AI doesn't just sit in a marketing deck. It transcribes calls, scores agent performance, and surfaces trends you'd never spot manually.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-cloudtalk"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
