      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Key Features That Make CloudTalk Shine",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Before diving into tips, let's cover the feature set — because knowing what's available shapes how you use it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Smart IVR (Interactive Voice Response)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CloudTalk's IVR builder is drag-and-drop. You can route callers by language, department, time of day, or even by the number they dialed. One SaaS client cut their average wait time from 4 minutes to 47 seconds just by redesigning their IVR tree inside CloudTalk.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Call Recording & Transcription",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every call can be recorded automatically. The transcription engine turns those recordings into searchable text. Managers can review a week's worth of calls in minutes instead of hours, pulling up specific keywords like \"discount\" or \"cancel\" to spot coaching opportunities.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Real-Time Analytics Dashboard",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Live dashboards show queue lengths, agent availability, average handle time, and conversion rates — all updating in real time. No more end-of-week spreadsheet scrambles.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Power Dialer & Click-to-Call",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For outbound teams, the power dialer chews through lists fast. Click-to-call works inside your CRM (Salesforce, HubSpot, Pipedrive, and more), so agents never copy-paste numbers again.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI-Powered Conversation Intelligence",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CloudTalk's AI flags calls where customers showed frustration, where agents missed upsell moments, and where scripts are working beautifully. It's like having a quality-assurance analyst who never sleeps.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-cloudtalk"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Want a step-by-step walkthrough on setting up these features? We've got a hands-on ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "how to use CloudTalk",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " tutorial ready for you.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
