        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Who Is CloudTalk Ideal For?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Not every tool fits every team. Here's where CloudTalk genuinely excels:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Sales Teams (SMB to Mid-Market)",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — If your reps make 40+ outbound calls a day and live inside a CRM, CloudTalk's click-to-call and power dialer will save them an hour daily. Period.",
