        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CloudTalk offers tiered pricing starting with a Starter plan for small teams, scaling up to Essential and Expert tiers with advanced features like AI call scoring and custom analytics. You can see current pricing and start a free trial at ",
