        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Almost certainly yes. CloudTalk has native, deep integrations with Salesforce, HubSpot, Pipedrive, Zendesk, Freshdesk, and dozens more. Bi-directional sync ensures your data stays consistent across platforms.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I use CloudTalk for both inbound and outbound calls?",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. CloudTalk handles both natively. You can run inbound support queues and outbound sales campaigns simultaneously from the same account, with separate dashboards and routing rules for each.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is CloudTalk suitable for remote teams?",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "It's built for them. The platform runs in any modern browser and offers iOS and Android apps. Agents can take calls from anywhere with an internet connection, and managers get full visibility through real-time dashboards.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How does CloudTalk's AI transcription work?",
            "marks": [
