        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every recorded call is automatically transcribed and analyzed. The AI identifies sentiment, keywords, talk-to-listen ratios, and conversation topics. Summaries and scores appear in your dashboard and sync to your CRM.",
